also get feedback in the form of comments or social media discussion and things like that.

00:05:38.799 --> 00:05:46.480
And then also to give updates and news and let other folks know what is going on in the world.

00:05:47.440 --> 00:05:54.799
But thinking about a data science community, specifically, blogs can really help showcase

00:05:54.799 --> 00:06:00.880
the kind of soft skills needed for data scientists. It can provide a platform to share,

