portfolio of work and makes it very easy to share, because everything is in one place.

00:06:15.040 --> 00:06:20.959
And it kind of centralizes your work, rather than having things in various different spots.

00:06:23.920 --> 00:06:29.519
And so when you watch those talks, and more generally, we often talk about reasons behind

