creating a personal blog, especially if you're looking for a job. But I also want to note that

00:06:35.279 --> 00:06:41.839
your team or organization could also benefit from having a blog. So external blogs, like the ones

00:06:41.839 --> 00:06:48.160
that we have at RStudio, are examples of these. Quick aside, just so you're aware, we have four

