00:50:04.080 --> 00:50:11.120
how-tos, and you can kind of create your work around that, but I do think it really, like,

00:50:11.679 --> 00:50:16.879
it depends on what you are interested in and what your goals are. Like I mentioned earlier,

00:50:17.760 --> 00:50:25.199
that if, like, somebody is searching for something, like, what do you want them to

00:50:26.080 --> 00:50:32.239
put into, you know, their search bar and be able to find, like, your post and consider it that way.

00:50:32.879 --> 00:50:38.000
So, that's for, like, the title. In terms of, like, the content within the post,

00:50:38.639 --> 00:50:44.159
there are also some guidelines that folks say, like, you don't want a blog post that's too long,

00:50:44.159 --> 00:50:48.239
but you don't want one that's too short and things like that, but I think it's more about

00:50:49.439 --> 00:50:57.760
displaying, like, what you really want and sometimes, you know, considering, like, oh,

00:50:57.760 --> 00:51:04.159
maybe this can be a series of posts as opposed to one particular post. Can you make it more

00:51:04.159 --> 00:51:08.959
engaging? If it's for a personal post, maybe, like, adding memes or, you know,

00:51:08.959 --> 00:51:16.479
funny images or things like that. If it's more serious, making sure that your headers are very

00:51:16.479 --> 00:51:21.760
clear, that somebody, you know, quickly going through the blog post can easily find the

00:51:21.760 --> 00:51:23.919
section that they're interested in and things like that.

